森県青森市大字荒川字柴田102番地1 お問合せはお気軽に TEL:017-739-2025\"></div>\n    </header>\n    <!-- / #header --></div>\n<ul id=\"navi\">\n<li class=\"home\"><a href=\"/\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/share/nav-home.gif\" alt=\"ホーム\" /></a></li>\n<li class=\"works\"><a href=\"/civilworks.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/share/nav-works.gif\" alt=\"業務紹介\" /></a></li>\n<li class=\"company\"><a href=\"/company.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/share/nav-company.gif\" alt=\"会社案内\" /></a></li>\n<li class=\"access\"><a href=\"/access.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/share/nav-access.gif\" alt=\"アクセス\" /></a></li>\n<li class=\"inquiry\"><a href=\"/inquiry.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/share/nav-inquiry.gif\" alt=\"お問合せ\" /></a></li>\n</ul><!--hero-->\n<div class=\"hero l-section\">\n    <div class=\"hero-tit fadeIn\">NISHIDA<div class=\"hero-subtit\">CHALLENGE FOR NEW VALUE CREATION</div></div>\n  <div class=\"swiper\">\n    <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n        <div class=\"slide\">\n          <div class=\"slide-media img-cover\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/hero01.jpg\" alt=\"NISHIDA｜西田組ウェブサイト｜土木工事/解体工事/産業・医療廃棄物/建築工事/環境対策事業/除雪事業\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n        <div class=\"slide\">\n          <div class=\"slide-media img-cover\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/hero02.jpg\" alt=\"NISHIDA｜西田組ウェブサイト｜土木工事/解体工事/産業・医療廃棄物/建築工事/環境対策事業/除雪事業\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n        <div class=\"slide\">\n          <div class=\"slide-media img-cover\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/hero03.jpg\" alt=\"NISHIDA｜西田組ウェブサイト｜土木工事/解体工事/産業・医療廃棄物/建築工事/環境対策事業/除雪事業\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n        <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n        <div class=\"slide\">\n          <div class=\"slide-media img-cover\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/hero04.jpg\" alt=\"NISHIDA｜西田組ウェブサイト｜土木工事/解体工事/産業・医療廃棄物/建築工事/環境対策事業/除雪事業\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div><!-- /swiper-wrapper -->\n    <div class=\"swiper-pagination\"></div>\n  </div><!-- /swiper -->\n</div>\n<script>\n  const mySwiper = new Swiper('.hero .swiper', {\n    effect: 'fade',\n    fadeEffect: {\n      crossFade: true,\n    },\n    loop: true,\n    loopAdditionalSlides: 1,\n    speed: 2000,\n    autoplay: {\n      delay: 7000,\n      disableOnInteraction: false,\n      waitForTransition: false,\n    },\n    followFinger: false,\n    pagination: {\n      el: '.hero .swiper-pagination',\n      clickable: true,\n    },\n  });\n</script>\n<!--/hero-->\n<div id=\"top-contents\">\n\n<div id=\"top-main\">\n\n<div class=\"section\">\n<h3><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-title-works.gif\" alt=\"業務紹介\"><a href=\"/civilworks.html\" class=\"img_wrap\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-btn-detail1.png\" alt=\"業務紹介詳細へ\" class=\"top-btn\"></a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"top-box\">\n<h4><a href=\"/civilworks.html\">土木工事</a></h4>\n<div class=\"works-icon\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-icon1.png\" alt=\"土木工事\"></div>\n<div class=\"top-box-btn img_wrap\"><a href=\"/civilworks.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-btn-detail2.png\" alt=\"土木工事詳細へ\"></a></div>\n<div class=\"top-works-photo img_wrap\"><a href=\"/civilworks.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-worksimg1.jpg\" alt=\"土木工事写真\"></a></div>\n<p class=\"top-works-text\">地域社会の安全性と災害防止に役立ち、社会資本の整備に貢献することを目指しています。</p>\n</div><!-- / 土木工事 -->\n\n<div class=\"top-box\">\n<h4><a href=\"/demolishwork.html\">解体工事</a></h4>\n<div class=\"works-icon\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-icon2.png\" alt=\"解体工事\"></div>\n<div class=\"top-box-btn img_wrap\"><a href=\"/demolishwork.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-btn-detail2.png\" alt=\"解体工事詳細へ\"></a></div>\n<div class=\"top-works-photo img_wrap\"><a href=\"/demolishwork.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-worksimg2.jpg\" alt=\"解体工事写真\"></a></div>\n<p class=\"top-works-text\">個人の家屋の解体から、特殊な工作物の解体まで、最適な解体方法を提案し、解体工事を行います。</p>\n</div><!-- / 解体工事 -->\n\n<div class=\"top-box-right\">\n<h4><a href=\"/garbagedisposal.html\">産業・医療廃棄物</a></h4>\n<div class=\"works-icon\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-icon3.png\" alt=\"産業・医療廃棄物\"></div>\n<div class=\"top-box-btn img_wrap\"><a href=\"/garbagedisposal.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-btn-detail2.png\" alt=\"産業・医療廃棄物処理詳細へ\"></a></div>\n<div class=\"top-works-photo img_wrap\"><a href=\"/garbagedisposal.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-worksimg3.jpg\" alt=\"産業・医療廃棄物処理写真\"></a></div>\n<p class=\"top-works-text\">出来る限り資源化し、循環型社会構築に資する様、産業・医療廃棄物の収集運搬・処理を行います。</p>\n</div><!-- / 産業・医療廃棄物 -->\n\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"top-boxS\">\n<h4><a href=\"/constructionwork.html\">建築工事</a></h4>\n<div class=\"works-icon\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-icon4.png\" alt=\"建築工事\"></div>\n<div class=\"top-box-btn img_wrap\"><a href=\"/constructionwork.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-btn-detail2.png\" alt=\"建築工事詳細へ\"></a></div>\n<div class=\"top-works-photoS img_wrap\"><a href=\"/constructionwork.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-worksimg4.jpg\" alt=\"建築工事写真\"></a></div>\n<p class=\"top-works-textS\">総合的な建築工事から、メンテナンスまでお任せ下さい。</p>\n</div>\n<!-- / 建築工事 -->\n\n<div class=\"top-boxS\">\n<h4><a href=\"/environment.html\">環境対策事業</a></h4>\n<div class=\"works-icon\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-icon5.png\" alt=\"環境対策事業\"></div>\n<div class=\"top-box-btn img_wrap\"><a href=\"/environment.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-btn-detail2.png\" alt=\"環境対策事業詳細へ\"></a></div>\n<div class=\"top-works-photoS img_wrap\"><a href=\"/environment.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-worksimg5.jpg\" alt=\"環境対策事業写真\"></a></div>\n<p class=\"top-works-textS\">解体に伴う有害物質除去など一貫した対応を行っています。</p>\n</div>\n<!-- / 環境対策事業 -->\n\n<div class=\"top-boxS-right\">\n<h4><a href=\"/ploughing.html\">除雪事業</a></h4>\n<div class=\"works-icon\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-icon6.png\" alt=\"除雪事業\"></div>\n<div class=\"top-box-btn img_wrap\"><a href=\"/ploughing.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-btn-detail2.png\" alt=\"除雪事業詳細へ\"></a></div>\n<div class=\"top-works-photoS img_wrap\"><a href=\"/ploughing.html\"><img src=\"http://www.nishidagumi.co.jp/contents/wp-content/themes/Nishidagumi/img/top/top-worksimg6.jpg\" alt=\"除雪事業写真\"></a></div>\n<p class=\"top-works-textS\">豪雪地帯の青森市でも安心して冬期を過ごせる街にします。</p>\n</div>\n<!-- / 除雪事業 -->\n</div><!-- / .section-->\n\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n\n<d